  <brief_title>Clinical Outcomes of Endoscopic Resection for Treating WHYX Lesion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Outcomes of Endoscopic Resection for Treating Extremely Well Differentiated Intestinal-type Adenocarcinoma (WHYX Lesion)</official_title>
