  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Endoscopically, WHYX cancers demonstrated a vague extent of tumor spread due to pale color
      changes in both the background atrophic and metaplastic gastric mucosa. However, the clinical
      outcomes of WHYX cancers after endoscopic resection are unknown. The aim of this study was to
      evaluate clinical outcomes of WHYX cancers after endoscopic resection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
