  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>complete resection rate</measure>
    <time_frame>6 months after endoscopical resection</time_frame>
    <description>Complete resection was defined to have all of the following features: 1. grossly en bloc resection, 2. Tumor-free lateral and vertical resection margins, 3. No lymphovascular invasion, and 5. A depth of submucosal tumor invasion of less than 500 micrometers.</description>
